bsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/wardrobe-design\/\">wardrobe designs<\/a>&nbsp;amongst Design Cafe customers.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Are there differences in wardrobe designs based on gender?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Swati Santani<\/strong>: Yes there are his and her wardrobes which ideally have different compositions. Men\u2019s wardrobes stack in more shirts, trousers and jackets and therefore more hangers work well. A few shelves and a couple of drawers for belts and tees usually suffice too.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>For women, one would prefer to use short, medium and long hanging space for folded sarees, skirts, shirts, short and long dresses. Hooks or smaller shelves for scarves, stoles, and accessories are also important. More drawers work well to store smaller items.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012534\/indian-bedroom-designs-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"Men and women latest wardrobe designs for bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-17618\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012534\/indian-bedroom-designs-wardrobe.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012534\/indian-bedroom-designs-wardrobe-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012534\/indian-bedroom-designs-wardrobe-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012534\/indian-bedroom-designs-wardrobe-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012534\/indian-bedroom-designs-wardrobe-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012534\/indian-bedroom-designs-wardrobe-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012534\/indian-bedroom-designs-wardrobe-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012534\/indian-bedroom-designs-wardrobe-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012534\/indian-bedroom-designs-wardrobe-70x70.jpg 70w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012534\/indian-bedroom-designs-wardrobe-140x140.jpg 140w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012534\/indian-bedroom-designs-wardrobe-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Various compartments and compositions in wardrobe design help in organising clothing and accessories<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Now let us talk about top wardrobe trends for 2024? What can we expect to dominate bedroom storage?<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Swati Santani<\/strong>: A clean, minimalist look for a clutter-free and better organised space is what will define 2024. Wardrobes are becoming as important as other spaces in the house. They are being treated like spaces in themselves and getting the attention they rightly deserve. A good wardrobe helps you begin your day trendy and stylishly.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012714\/sliding-wardrobe-designs-bedroom.jpg\" alt=\"Sliding wardrobe design for bedroom in minimalist look with a rustic touch\" class=\"wp-image-17619\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012714\/sliding-wardrobe-designs-bedroom.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012714\/sliding-wardrobe-designs-bedroom-150x150.jpg 150w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012714\/sliding-wardrobe-designs-bedroom-300x300.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012714\/sliding-wardrobe-designs-bedroom-768x768.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012714\/sliding-wardrobe-designs-bedroom-415x415.jpg 415w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012714\/sliding-wardrobe-designs-bedroom-417x416.jpg 417w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012714\/sliding-wardrobe-designs-bedroom-225x225.jpg 225w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012714\/sliding-wardrobe-designs-bedroom-475x475.jpg 475w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012714\/sliding-wardrobe-designs-bedroom-70x70.jpg 70w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012714\/sliding-wardrobe-designs-bedroom-140x140.jpg 140w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/12\/18012714\/sliding-wardrobe-designs-bedroom-200x200.jpg 200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">This wardrobe with textures and wood is a minimalist wardrobe design for those who love clean looks<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>As we\u2019ve seen from Swati\u2019s insights, wardrobes are going to ride the wave in&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/\">home designs for 2024<\/a>. So if you\u2019re planning a home transformation, your wardrobe must feature in it prominently. Reach out to us at Design Cafe to give you the style and look that will complement and transform your bedroom.<\/p>\n\n\n\n\n\n<p>Explore, More About<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/sliding-wardrobe-design-ideas\/\">Sliding Wardrobe Design Ideas<\/a><\/li>\n\n\n\n<li><a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/wooden-wardrobe-design-ideas\/\">Wooden Wardrobe Designs For Bedroom<\/a><\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend ali